  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is planning to develop the audiovisual videos and determine whether educational
      videos are superior to routine discussion for informing trauma patients in emergency
      department (ED) about risks, benefits, and alternatives to receiving surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
